Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:52.64,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The masters of common sense are laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:58.64,Concert-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}What lie will they tell next?
